des:
This skill can help you look for homes in Michigan. The skill will ask some simple questions to find out your preferences, then email you houses that match your search. Start a different search or come back later to get updated on new houses on the market that fit your last search. You can also ask to sell your home, and the Tina Peterson team will calculate an estimate on your house. 

I believe our success comes from being honest, hardworking and willing to go the extra mile to make sure all aspects of getting your home sold have been taken care of! The Tina Peterson Team is now offering an Alexa Skill that can help you buy or sell a home in Michigan. This skill will ask some basic questions about your home buying presences, then email you matching results. This skill is great for someone starting the home buying experience or if you would like to get a quote on your house. The skill will also email Tina Peterson at Real Estate One so she can further assist you in your home buying or selling.
